Based on the execution logs, here is the report:

EXISTING STRUCTURES

### Iron Plate Production Line
Consists of two furnaces for smelting iron plates:
- Furnace at position (0.0, 0.0)
- Furnace at position (2.0, 0.0)

### Copper Plate Production Line
Consists of two furnaces for smelting copper plates:
- Furnace at position (4.0, 4.0)
- Furnace at position (6.0, 4.0)

### Power Generation System
Steam-based power generation setup consisting of:
- Offshore pump at position (-9.5, 24.5)
- Boiler at position (-2.5, 24.0)
- Steam engine at position (4.5, 24.5)
- Two pipe groups:
  - Water pipes connecting offshore pump to boiler (fluid system 2237)
  - Steam pipes connecting boiler to steam engine (fluid system 2239)
- Electric pole network connecting power to other structures (electricity group 2344)

### Research Lab
Lab at position (10.5, 0.5) conducting research on logistics technology

ERROR TIPS

### Inventory Full Errors
- Check available space in target inventory before attempting to insert items
- Extract items from full inventories before attempting to add more

### Missing Resources Errors
- Ensure required resources are in inventory before attempting crafting or insertion operations
- Harvest more resources when running low

### Research Prerequisite Errors
- Check technology prerequisites before attempting to research advanced technologies
- Research basic technologies first before attempting to research their upgrades

### Power System Errors
- Monitor boiler fuel levels regularly
- Add fuel to boiler before it runs completely empty to maintain continuous power generation

### No Research Progress Errors
- Verify research is actually selected before checking research progress
- Handle cases where no research is in progress appropriately
